 The unit of the answer should be  .
Solution: ## Step 1
To find $P(52.761 \leq \bar{X} \leq 54.453)$, we first need to understand that $\bar{X}$, the sample mean, follows a normal distribution due to the Central Limit Theorem since the sample size $n = 47$ is sufficiently large.

## Step 2
