## Step 8
$P(-1.50 \leq Z \leq 0.50) = P(Z \leq 0.50) - P(Z \leq -1.50)$. Using a standard normal distribution table: $P(Z \leq 0.50) = 0.6915$ and $P(Z \leq -1.50) = 0.0668$.

